[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man and girl, 8, killed in Wakefield house fire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man and an eight-year-old girl have died in a house fire, police have said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 42-year-old man and the girl died when a blaze broke out at a house in Ash Crescent, in the Stanley area of Wakefield, at about 04:20 BST.
A woman, 35, and a 13-year-old girl who were also in the house were treated in hospital for non-life threatening injuries before being discharged.
West Yorkshire Police said an investigation into the cause of the fire was under way.
